cast.overview: The story of Gary Valentine and Alana Kane growing up, running around and going through the treacherous navigation of first love in the San Fernando Valley, 1973.
cast.title: Licorice Pizza

details.biography: Alana Mychal Haim (born December 15, 1991) is an American musician and actress. She is a pianist, guitarist, and vocalist of the American pop-rock band Haim, which also consists of her two older sisters, Este Haim and Danielle Haim. In 2021, she starred in Paul Thomas Anderson's film Licorice Pizza alongside Cooper Hoffman and the rest of Haim.
details.name: Alana Haim
